_sText:
Welcome to Two Towers!

Disclaimer:  I understand that there are many remakes of this map floating around, but I don't feel that any of them did the original justice.  I took the original .vmf and rebuilt it from scratch.  It is fully optimized and has a brand new feel to it.

Credits:  Credits for original design and build go to Smurf™.

Changes:
-Noticeable texture scheme change
-Aesthetic changes throughout the entire map IE: stairs instead of ramps at certain places/wall changes etc.
-Optimized to the best of my ability, for smoother game-play
-Other changes

All in all, I hope this remake will be worth while for all the fanatics out there.  New feel, runs smoother, and still just as fun to play!

Comments and ratings are always appreciated!


-:Gaiy-P§ycho:
